These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: traveling, writing
House: farmhouse, modern
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: soccer, volleyball
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: dahlia, balloon-flower
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
3. the farmhouse house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Hobby       | writing       | traveling |
| House         | modern | farmhouse  |
| Sport       | volleyball    | soccer    |
| Flower   | balloon-flower       | dahlia      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: dahlia, amaryllis
The people have 2 different jobs:  entrepreneur, lawyer
There 2 different types of food: onion, blueberry
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: snowboarding, surfing
1. the person eating onion is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the entrepreneur is on the far left##1
3. the person eating onion is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Flower      | amaryllis     | dahlia |
| Job           | entrepreneur | lawyer      |
| Food   | blueberry  | onion      |
| Sport         | snowboarding | surfing     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, soy-milk
There 2 different types of food: apple, avocado
The people have 2 different hobbies: puzzles, rock-climbing
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: weightlifting, cycling
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who's sport is cycling##1
3. the person eating apple is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | soy-milk  |
| Food          | apple    | avocado   |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing  | puzzles   |
| Sport     | cycling     | weightlifting |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, soy-milk
There are 2 different favourite colors: white, purple
House: palace, colonial
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: punk, techno
1. the fan of punk is on the far left##1
2. the palace house is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is the person who likes white##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea       | soy-milk |
| Color          | purple         | white    |
| House           | colonial | palace    |
| Music-Genre   | punk           | techno   |

