The people prefer 2 different music-genres: classical, country
There are 2 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, iced-tea
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: superhero, disaster
1. the fan of classical is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Hobby         | skydiving | video-games   |
| Music-Genre   | classical | country       |
| Beverage         | soy-milk   | iced-tea |
| Movie-Genre     | disaster    | superhero     |

