2 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, chaman
2 different pets are kept: mouse, rabbit
2 different games are played: chess, bridge
1. the coach is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
2. the coach is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
3. the owner of the mouse is the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Job           | security-guard | coach     |
| Cigar   | tiparillo          | chaman |
| Pet           | mouse          | rabbit    |
| Game     | bridge            | chess       |

 